462
00:50:38,120 --> 00:50:40,846
<i>All four Red Sox runs in the 2nd.</i>

463
00:51:42,920 --> 00:51:44,804
You fool.

464
00:52:33,560 --> 00:52:37,119
<i>Tonight at 11:00, more on
