473
00:53:21,880 --> 00:53:23,799
Did you have a good time today?

474
00:53:23,800 --> 00:53:25,331
Yee-yeah!

475
00:53:25,440 --> 00:53:26,639
<i>This is Lynn Jolicoeur</i>

476
00:53:26,640 --> 00:53:27,879
